      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国被要求逆转苏纳克的绿色回滚政策以实现净零排放目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/uk-told-to-reverse-sunak-s-green-rollback-to-meet-net-zero-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家气候监督机构表示，新工党政府必须“紧急”扭转其保守党前任对绿色能源计划的倒退，以实现英国的净零目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/uk-told-to-reverse-sunak-s-green-rollback-to-meet-net-zero-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
